398
00:27:31.902 --> 00:27:37.449
Did I ever question the hours and days
you spent away in service of the Silo?

399
00:27:38.116 --> 00:27:39.427
-When Juliette's waving...
-It...

400
00:27:39.451 --> 00:27:40.887
-a gun in our direction.
